f02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"band5-020-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"심사원 1","body":"맞아요. 그러니까 더더욱… 여러분은\n이 콘테스트에서 「입상」해서 페스티벌에 나갈 게 아니라\n「우승」해서 메인 스테이지에 갔으면 해요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"전원","body":"……!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"band5-020-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"심사원 2","body":"FUTURE WORLD FES.가 단순한 페스티벌이 아니라는 건\n알고 계시겠죠.\n우리는 이 장르의 성장을  원칙으로 운영합니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"심사원 1","body":"당신들은 아직 젊고 비주얼도 좋아.\n분명 화제가 되겠죠.\n하지만 이 장르를 위해서는 「지금」은 아니에요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"심사원 2","body":"결성한 지 얼마 안 됐고, 연습 기간도 짧아서 상당히 거친 부분이 있는데도\n우리를 이렇게나 매료시켰어요.\nRoselia, 여러분의 잠재력은 아주 커요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motio